<HEAD>Payments Headed for Corn, Sorghum Growers</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Corn and sorghum growers who participated in
last year's feed grain program will get about $125 million in
federal payments this month, the Agriculture Department said
Thursday.
