<FIRST>u f PM-TexasEastern CORRECTIVE   03-02 0092</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Texas Eastern, CORRECTIVE,0094</SECOND>
<HEAD>Eds: Members who used PM-Texas Eastern, transmitted as f0065 on Wednesday,
March 2, are asked to use the following story.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>HOUSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The Associated Press on Wednesday erroneously
identified Robert D. Hunsucker as chairman of Texas Eastern Corp.
Hunsucker is chairman, chief executive and president of Panhandle
Eastern Corp.
   The error occurred in a story regarding the sale of Texas
Eastern's oil and gas production and exploration units to a British
petroleum company for about $1.4 billion, to help finance Texas
Eastern's acquisition by Panhandle Eastern.
</TEXT>
